    {
      "bookmarkId": "834464_29_30022-30115",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "30022-30115",
      "markText": "谁料到我一走凤霞就出事了，我走了才几分钟，好几个医生跑进了产房，还拖着氧气瓶。凤霞生下了孩子后大出血，天黑前断了气。我的一双儿女都是生孩子上死的，有庆死是别人生孩子，凤霞死在自己生孩子。",
      "totalCount": 42444,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=834464&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=30022&rangeEnd=30115",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33332bf05cbba0333b1efb4?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=30022&rangeEnd=30115"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "834464_30_4614-4680",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "4614-4680",
      "markText": "这样的日子过到苦根四岁那年，二喜死了。二喜是被两排水泥板夹死的。干搬运这活，一不小心就磕破碰伤，可丢了命的只有二喜，徐家的人命都苦。",
      "totalCount": 38790,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=834464&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=4614&rangeEnd=4680",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33332bf05cbba0333b1efb4?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=4614&rangeEnd=4680"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "834464_26_4060-4115",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "4060-4115",
      "markText": "“我怕它知道只有自己在耕田，就多叫出几个名字去骗它，它听到还有别的牛也在耕田，就不会不高兴，耕田也就起劲啦。”",
      "totalCount": 34080,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=834464&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=4060&rangeEnd=4115",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33332bf05cbba0333b1efb4?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=4060&rangeEnd=4115"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "834464_29_29723-29852",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "29723-29852",
      "markText": "“生啦，是儿子。” 二喜一听急了，跳起来叫道： “我没要小的。” 医生说：“大的也没事。”",
      "totalCount": 32850,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=834464&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=29723&rangeEnd=29852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33332bf05cbba0333b1efb4?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=29723&rangeEnd=29852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "834464_28_28703-28774",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "28703-28774",
      "markText": "“你给我、给你娘你姐姐争了口气，我很高兴。可我从没听说过跑步也能挣饭吃，送你去学校，是要你好好念书，不是让你去学跑步，跑步还用学？鸡都会跑！”",
      "totalCount": 31348,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=834464&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=28703&rangeEnd=28774",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33332bf05cbba0333b1efb4?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=28703&rangeEnd=28774"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "834464_30_14667-14758",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "14667-14758",
      "markText": "“今天有庆、二喜耕了一亩，家珍、凤霞耕了也有七八分田，苦根还小都耕了半亩。你嘛，耕了多少我就不说了，说出来你会觉得我是要羞你。话还得说回来，你年纪大了，能耕这么些田也是尽心尽力了。”",
      "totalCount": 29631,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=834464&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=14667&rangeEnd=14758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33332bf05cbba0333b1efb4?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=14667&rangeEnd=14758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "834464_30_14871-14889",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "14871-14889",
      "markText": "少年去游荡，中年想掘藏，老年做和尚。",
      "totalCount": 27417,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=834464&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=14871&rangeEnd=14889",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33332bf05cbba0333b1efb4?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=14871&rangeEnd=14889"
